* install dependencies
** components listed in setup.py's install_requires
** tiddlywebplugins.devstore
* extend hosts file (e.g. /etc/hosts) to include one or more subdomains, e.g.:
    127.0.0.1 localhost foo.localhost bar.localhost
* create development instance:
    $ make dev
    $ cd dev_instance
    $ twanager server 0.0.0.0 8080
    # open http://localhost:8080 in web browser
* changes to *.js within the repository files are reflected directly in the
  browser (after a page reload)
* deploy: $ make deploy

also see STYLE guide
